node.text:
Kamala Devi Harris. First Female. First Black. First South Asian. First woman of color to be VP. The first — but as she told me and @barackobama on the campaign trail — not the last. 

This is Beyond representation — this is power ⚡️ Madam Vice President, you are not alone . We are all in that room with you. #HERstory  @kamalaharris

node.text:
The only limitations that exist are the ones that you create in your mind. This marketing agency has been something that I always dreamed of, because we know how important it is for us to be a part of these convos. 

That’s why @Jus_Chad and I founded @Obsidianworks. Now in partnership with @160over90, we’re committed to creating lasting impact and opening doors of opportunity.
